Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去 人們曾對妖怪心存畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而走在妖怪們前面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領軍「百鬼夜行」的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們稱之為妖怪的總帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賦予其別稱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魑魅魍魎之主——「滑頭鬼」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您果然來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來您確實是繼承了總帥之血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過一到白天 您又會變回人類的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且忘記自己身為妖怪之事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是白天的您並不知道現在這副模樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說您夜晚和白天是完全不同的兩人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 就這麼在意我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我的妖怪之血覺醒時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法就沒有改變過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成為三代頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立於你們之上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風姿颯爽的夜陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年紀輕輕又有些隨性而為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佇立於萬妖之巔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他究竟能否擁有真正的「畏」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\3c&H6F1317&}「畏」：身為妖怪 讓人感到恐嚇、威嚴、或尊敬之念\N是作為妖怪的存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要跟隨我之後成為百鬼夜行之眾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(200,0)\bord3\be4\3c&H27275F&}成為魑魅魍魎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家都到齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴良組手下全數到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人欣喜啊 少爺竟然會召集我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下真是行了「手下運」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著實符合三代頭目該有的行事舉止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒那回事……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 陸生少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論打架鬥毆 請儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是有事拜託才叫大家過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事拜託?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺拜託我們?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚大家絕對不能接近我那所中學的舊校舍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舊校舍就是學校後面的那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這又是出於什麼緣由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你們絕對不能接近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 陸生今天挺早的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便當還沒準備……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在小賣部買點啥吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請留步 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世間險惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少請帶上刀以作護身之用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了啦 我就是去上個學嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛……牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是少主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好……好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近來可好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙少主關心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得見少主安泰 不勝安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛鬼不論何時都那麼可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛鬼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭候多時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛鬼大人不會想撇開少爺自己當三代頭目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會容許這種事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多日未見 總帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛鬼你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說身形模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生大人連思想也與人類一致
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們妖怪都深受人類敬畏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是擁有真正的「畏」的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這行事困難的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是確認我們對代紋所發的誓言之時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺不繼承奴良組的話……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不要跟著我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎~呀~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我才不管什麼妖怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要作為普通人類……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}你們聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個有關舊校舍的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舊校舍? 有什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然屬於學校用地 卻沒什麼人去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說有妖怪出沒……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能有妖怪什麼的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧？陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你們幾個 今晚沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了 清繼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴良也會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們決定今晚去舊校舍探險！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要去找出妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清繼真喜歡關於妖怪的故事哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 舊校舍有妖怪的謠言是你傳出來的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是謠言！四年前我親眼見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪確實存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪什麼的不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說你們幾個害怕妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊 沒什麼怕不怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不太清楚妖怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧？陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們幾個也來參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是瞭解妖怪的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但……但是女孩子的話會很危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正妖怪什麼的根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 今晚你就會瞭解到妖怪的存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天有跟家裏那些傢伙說過別接近舊校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:10:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來玩吧 來玩吧 來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 今晚稍微有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}來玩嘛 來玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒勁 真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們幹活去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁晚上把庭院掃乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那爺爺 我和朋友出去……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事啊 爺爺 我急著和朋友出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 有想繼承三代頭目的想法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又說這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你問幾次我的想法都不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你繼承了我四分之一的血統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣 我也要作為人類生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就決定了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 要出去嗎 路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若菜 再添一碗飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人毛骨悚然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果害怕馬上告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不存在什麼妖怪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種不詳的預感是怎麼回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟他們說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真……真的要進去嗎？清繼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著就像是有妖怪出沒的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊 有啊 這裏絕對有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有點怕誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心加奈 今晚不會有妖怪出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 總之不管發生什麼我絕對會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家別怕 只是幅畫而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先檢查下這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴良檢查下那邊的架子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誒 真的有誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不是我們組的妖怪出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來到底是哪個組的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱水室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好……好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼呀奴良
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不……不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…… 突然口很渴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想喝血 好想喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在起我走最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊看起來也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才起怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒……沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據我的調查絕對應該有妖怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然根本不存在什麼妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一開始不就說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 全是我沒見過的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去大家就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 最後看看這裏就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要這裏沒有……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好……這裏很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本保護不了加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青田坊真是的 動作太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生少爺請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來保護您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准動少爺一根汗毛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來當你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總帥 二代頭目都死了多少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能總讓早已退隱的您一直代理總帥的位置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事 就如我每次所說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統率奴良組72團旗下1萬妖怪的三代頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我孫子陸生別無他選
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是陸生少爺尚且年幼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據在下所聞 陸生少爺自己並無此意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總帥 這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他做為妖怪覺醒 也只有四年前的一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誠如大家所言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂「畏」 即寫作執鬼之鞭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是黑暗世界之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜待便可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生少爺執鞭之日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是真正的「畏」降臨之時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺 我們從四年前的那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在您身邊保護著您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在少爺的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有話等下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點離開這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家也好 在外面也好 在學校也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從夜陸生少爺覺醒的那天起 我們一直都在少爺身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個樣子您有印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1班的及川和倉田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 還是得請您繼承三代頭目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會一直等待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待像四年前那天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生少爺再次立於我們 妖怪百鬼夜行之上的日子降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不記得那天的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已決心做為一個人類活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪 怪物……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有妖怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快點去寫作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我再晚點闖進去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定能看到少爺的覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那些了 快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 茶泡好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勞您費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是位招人喜歡的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能娶到你這樣的新娘的話就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉瞬即逝的妖怪之容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴良陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執鬼之鞭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的「畏」降臨之日何時才會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺的腦袋從什麼時候起變那麼長的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為啊 自打我開始掉頭髮以後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋就相應變長了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遲早有一天也會像我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑頭鬼之孫 毒羽飛舞於竹林

